msgstr ""
"When specified，this 设置 overrides the subdirectory rules (except the base "
"directory) defined中the DVR 配置和puts all 录像 done由this entry into the "
"subdirectory named here。See Help用于more info."

#: src/input/mpegts/iptv/iptv.c:857
